  <div class="question-body">
    <b>Question 1</b>
    <p>The flowchart represents an algorithm that performs a process on groups of values that are input.
    The algorithm will fail if the first value of any group is 0.
    An input of -1 will terminate the algorithm.</p>
    
    <img src="https://drive.google.com/uc?id=1Ht3jIbR1i8heKn_BXQnq4dQGp8oLsI6R" alt="Flowchart for Question 1">
    
    <p>(a) Complete the trace table for the input data:
    25, 35, 3, 0, 57, 20, 25, 18, 0, -1, 307, 40, 0</p>
    <p>(b) Describe the purpose of the algorithm.</p>
  </div>
  <span class="marks">[7 marks]</span>
</button>
<div class="panel">
  <div class="panel-content">
