        <td></td>
        <td></td>
        <td></td>
        <td></td>
      </tr>
    </table>
    <b>Answer (b) (2 marks)</b>
    <p>Any two from:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>to add together / find the average of a batch of numbers</li>
      <li>the total and average are output (when the batch is complete/when 0 is entered)</li>
      <li>when 0 is entered a new batch is started.</li>
    </ul>
