      </tr>
    </table>
    <b>Answer (b) (3 marks)</b>
    <ul>
      <li>Counts the number of accepted parts</li>
      <li>Counts the number of rejected parts</li>
      <li>Outputs the counts when an empty string is entered</li>
    </ul>
