<button class="accordion">
  <div class="question-body">
    <b>Question 4</b>
    <p>An algorithm is written in pseudocode:</p>
<pre class="pseudocode">
C = 1
WHILE C < 5
    IF X[C] > X[C+1]
        THEN
            T = X[C]
            X[C] = X[C+1]
            X[C+1] = T
    ENDIF
    C = C + 1
ENDWHILE
</pre>
    <p>Complete the trace table for the array X: 5, 2, 4, 3, 1</p>
  </div>
  <span class="marks">[6 marks]</span>
</button>
<div class="panel">
  <div class="panel-content">
    <b>Answer (6 marks)</b>
    <table>
      <tr>
        <th>C</th>
        <th>T</th>
